"System will automatically apply the B2B discount of 7% by the Sales Price "
"List \"<font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Wholesale (B2B)</font>\"."
msgstr ""
"Systemet anvender automatisk B2B-rabatten på 7 % via salgsprislisten \"<font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Engros (B2B)</font>\"."

