"Upon validation of the receipt, the system automatically sets the locations "
"(Racks) for the particular products received. \"<font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Acetratine 10 mg</font>” product will be stored at \"\n"
"            <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">WH/Stock/Rack 2</font>”."
